line=428 fonts=F0-12.0 bbox=108.0,127.0,503.54,139.0           :       Again, this contrast is exactly what one would expect, given our proposal. The
line=429 fonts=F0-12.0 iscore=0.14 bbox=72.0,115.0,504.24,127.0:claim is that verbs express propositional functions that take an individual as an argument,
line=430 fonts=F0-12.0 iscore=0.21 bbox=72.0,103.0,502.82,115.0:whereas  adjectives are  themselves  argumentless  individuals.  Now   the standard
line=431 fonts=F0-12.0 iscore=0.09 bbox=72.0,91.0,503.42,103.0 :assumption is that, all things being equal, nominalizations preserve the argument-taking
