line=527 fonts=F0-12.0 bbox=144.0,667.99,541.1,679.99             :              The same  effect can be seen on a larger scale by considering comparative Kwa
line=528 fonts=F0-12.0 iscore=0.21 bbox=108.0,655.99,539.18,667.99:       syntax, following Déchaine 1993. Déchaine  points out that the Yoruba language is very
line=529 fonts=F0-12.0 iscore=0.21 bbox=108.0,643.99,540.08,655.99:       rich in Serial Verb Constructions, (40b) being a simple example.  At the same  time,
line=530 fonts=F0-12.0 iscore=0.29 bbox=108.0,631.99,538.87,643.99:       Yoruba  is extremely poor in inflectional morphology: it reportedly has no inflectional
line=531 fonts=F0-12.0 iscore=0.20 bbox=108.0,619.99,539.69,631.99:       affixes at all, tense and aspect being indicated by preverbal auxiliaries, by adverbs, or not
line=532 fonts=F0-12.0 iscore=0.13 bbox=108.0,607.99,189.3,619.99 :       at all (see (40a)).

